Pump Sales & Rental















Infusystem







































Pump Sales & Rental






HomePump Sales & Rental









InfuSystem® has the pumps you need to fit your budget, on-time and patient-ready.
Call Today  (800) 658-5582


“InfuSystem is who I rely on for all my infusion pump needs."
"When I call InfuSystem for rental pumps, the Customer Care team always makes it so quick and painless! A live person answers the phone, which allows my questions to get answered immediately. When necessary, I receive the infusion pump the next morning and the device is always clean and has all the proper paperwork attached.”
- Eli Ayala, Greystone Health Network 


As the leader in oncology and alternate site infusion, InfuSystem provides infusion services that fit your treatment protocols, staff preferences and budget parameters. We can help you determine the best pump and range of service for your needs.
InfuSystem offers its customers flexibility when it comes to their pole-mounted and ambulatory pump requirements. As your partner in care, InfuSystem works with your practice to ensure that your infusion pump fleet meets your expectations, and operates accurately and efficiently when you need it – the same goes for supplies and maintenance.
Our pump experts will tailor an infusion pump solution to fit your clinic’s needs and budget. Flexible financing options let you rent, lease, or buy new and pre-owned equipment. InfuSystem stocks over 60 makes and models from the most reputable manufacturers, all available with our worry-free 90-day warranty. Our pre-owned pumps are reconditioned and re-certified by our biomedical technicians to exacting specifications.
InfuSystem is your partner for pole mounted and ambulatory infusion pumps, supplies and service nationwide.
Ask your InfuSystem pump expert how drug libraries and smart pumps, from manufacturers such as Baxter, B. Braun Medical, Carefusion and Zyno, can improve your workflow, saving you time and money. You can easily add to your smart-pump fleet with InfuSystem rentals.
Some of our most popular IV pumps include:



Alaris 7130 and 7230 Signature Series
Baxter FloGard 6201
CADD Legacy PLUS




CADD Prizm 6101
Curlin 4000 CMS
Hospira Acclaim




Sigma Spectrum
Vista Basic





Contact InfuSystem® today to learn how our pump experts can help you find the right pump.  Call us toll-free (800) 658-5582.  *Not all items are available in Canada.





